# idea2product Cursor Rule

Follow `agent-adapters/common/IDEA2PRODUCT_AGENT_GUIDE.md` when the user asks for idea2product, product strategy, PRD-to-architecture handoff, staged delivery, gates, resume, or status.

Do not approve gates autonomously. In light mode (default) you may record the user's explicit in-chat approval (`pipeline_gate.py approve <gate> --rationale "…"`); in strict mode ask the user to approve in a real terminal. Never approve without the user's explicit decision.
